snippet.title: Mission Zero | Character Trailer: Aya
snippet.description:
As an energetic high school girl from the underground city, Aya has a great athletic talent. Her fashionable and cool style is widely loved by everyone. She often hums a nursery rhyme as well as swings her bat to threaten enemies. 
------------------------------------
The Technical Test will start on July 8th. Please follow us to get the first-hand information! 
- Pre-register now: https://www.missionzero.game/
- Discord: https://discord.gg/tQZTBYwgRC
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Missionzerogame
